<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
</head>
<body onmousemove="move();" style="width:700px; height:700px;">
  <script>
    function move() {
    e = window.event; 
    mouse_x = e.clientX;
    mouse_y = e.clientY;
    document.getElementById("x").value = mouse_x;
    document.getElementById("y").value = mouse_y;
    }   
  </script>
  <form> 마우스를 이동해 보세요. <br><br> Mouse Position: (X,Y)=( 
  <input id="x" size="3" type="text/">, <input id="y" size="3" type="text" />) 
  </form>
</body>
</html>
